Sun Met celebrated with G.H Mumm has announced that the retired sprinting legend will host of Africa's Richest Race Day next year. Stylish fashion, horse racing and entertainment are some of the highlights that visitors can expect at the show. The glitzy event will be run at Kenilworth Racecourse on Saturday, 27 January 2018. The theme for this year's race is Style Ahead of the Field. Tickets to the Sun Met will be on sale through TicketPro from the 19th October. Visit http://www.sunmet.co.za/  for more information.